---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Arquitectura | Core Nexus Five"
  description="Mapa conceptual interactivo de la arquitectura de datos en AWS: S3, Glue, Athena y más."
  pubDate={new Date("May 16 2026")}
  heroImage="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg"
>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Caveat:wght@400;500;700;800&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet"
  />

  <section class="architecture-wrapper">

    <div class="info-intro-card">
      <div class="card-shadow"></div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <h4 class="card-main-title">EL OLIMPO DE LOS DATOS</h4>
        <p class="card-subtitle-hint">
          Este mapa conceptual interactivo desarma nuestra arquitectura desde su base para comprender su lógica.
        </p>
        <p class="card-hover-cta">
          ↗ Pasa el cursor sobre los círculos para iluminar el halo de luz y revelar el popup explicativo.
        </p>
        <div class="analogy-box">
          <span class="handwritten-title">¿Por qué la analogía clásica?</span>
          <p class="analogy-body">La infraestructura de AWS opera sobre abstracciones complejas de red, computación y almacenamiento de datos. Implementamos esta capa conceptual basada en la Grecia Clásica no como decoración, sino como un modelo mental unificado. Al asociar servicios nativos en la nube con arquetipos universales, aceleramos la comprensión de la arquitectura, humanizamos los flujos de datos y transformamos la documentación técnica en una narrativa lógica y visual.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <svg class="architecture-lines" viewBox="0 0 1000 1300" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <defs>
        <linearGradient id="diagonal-pulse-gradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
          <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#ffffff" stop-opacity="0.2" />
          <stop offset="50%" stop-color="#ffffff" stop-opacity="1" />
          <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#ffffff" stop-opacity="0.2" />
        </linearGradient>
      </defs>
      <line x1="500" y1="125" x2="680" y2="227" class="side-map-line static-base" />
      <line x1="320" y1="572" x2="500" y2="395" class="side-map-line static-base" />
      <line x1="680" y1="572" x2="500" y2="395" class="side-map-line static-base" />
      <line x1="500" y1="125" x2="680" y2="227" class="side-map-line pulse-diagonal" />
      <line x1="320" y1="572" x2="500" y2="395" class="side-map-line pulse-diagonal" />
      <line x1="680" y1="572" x2="500" y2="395" class="side-map-line pulse-diagonal" />
    </svg>

    <div class="node node-large node-s3">
      <div class="node-content">
        <img src="/s3-logo.png" alt="S3" class="node-logo" />
      </div>
      <div class="node-popup popup-left">
        <div class="popup-header">
          <span class="popup-deity">Gaia</span>
          <span class="popup-aws-badge">AWS S3</span>
        </div>
        <p class="popup-body">S3 actúa como la raíz primordial del almacenamiento, donde se origina y asienta todo el ecosistema de datos.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="map-side-note note-right-large-node">
        <svg class="marker-arrow" viewBox="0 0 120 80">
          <path d="M-20,40 Q30,35 110,40" stroke="#d3d3d3" stroke-width="7.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <path d="M80,15 L112,41 L80,65" stroke="#d3d3d3" stroke-width="7.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="note-text-block">
          <span class="service-title-handwritten">S3</span>
          <span class="map-handwritten-text">Almacenamiento raíz<br>del sistema</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="node node-small node-side-right node-iam">
      <div class="node-content">
        <img src="/iam-logo.png" alt="IAM" class="node-logo" />
      </div>
      <div class="node-popup popup-left">
        <div class="popup-header">
          <span class="popup-deity">Cerbero</span>
          <span class="popup-aws-badge">AWS IAM</span>
        </div>
        <p class="popup-body">IAM custodia y gestiona los accesos de seguridad periférica de todo el ecosistema.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="map-side-note note-right-small-node">
        <svg class="marker-arrow" viewBox="0 0 120 80">
          <path d="M-20,40 Q30,35 110,40" stroke="#d3d3d3" stroke-width="7.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <path d="M80,15 L112,41 L80,65" stroke="#d3d3d3" stroke-width="7.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="note-text-block">
          <span class="service-title-handwritten">IAM</span>
          <span class="map-handwritten-text">Guardián de la<br>seguridad perimetral</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="node node-medium node-buckets">
      <div class="node-content">
        <img src="/bucket-logo.png" alt="Buckets" class="node-logo" />
      </div>
      <div class="node-popup popup-left">
        <div class="popup-header">
          <span class="popup-deity">Pandora</span>
          <span class="popup-aws-badge">S3 Buckets</span>
        </div>
        <p class="popup-body">Contenedores de datos específicos. Mal configurados desatan problemas, bien custodiados albergan valor.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="map-side-note note-right-medium-node">
        <svg class="marker-arrow" viewBox="0 0 120 80">
          <path d="M-20,40 Q30,35 110,40" stroke="#d3d3d3" stroke-width="7.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <path d="M80,15 L112,41 L80,65" stroke="#d3d3d3" stroke-width="7.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="note-text-block">
          <span class="service-title-handwritten">BUCKETS</span>
          <span class="map-handwritten-text">Depósitos de datos<br>críticos estructurados</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="node node-small node-side-left node-lambda">
      <div class="node-content">
        <img src="/lambda-logo.png" alt="Lambda" class="node-logo" />
      </div>
      <div class="node-popup popup-right">
        <div class="popup-header">
          <span class="popup-deity">Zeus</span>
          <span class="popup-aws-badge">AWS Lambda</span>
        </div>
        <p class="popup-body">Cómputo serverless inmediato que lanza rayos de código de manera reactiva bajo demanda.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="map-side-note note-left-small-node">
        <svg class="marker-arrow reverse-arrow" viewBox="0 0 120 80">
          <path d="M140,40 Q90,35 10,40" stroke="#d3d3d3" stroke-width="7.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <path d="M40,15 L8,41 L40,65" stroke="#d3d3d3" stroke-width="7.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="note-text-block">
          <span class="service-title-handwritten">LAMBDA</span>
          <span class="map-handwritten-text">Código reactivo<br>bajo demanda</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="node node-small node-side-right node-crawlers">
      <div class="node-content">
        <img src="/crawler-logo.png" alt="Crawlers" class="node-logo" />
      </div>
      <div class="node-popup popup-left">
        <div class="popup-header">
          <span class="popup-deity">Argos</span>
          <span class="popup-aws-badge">Glue Crawlers</span>
        </div>
        <p class="popup-body">Explora automáticamente las fuentes de datos mapeando y estructurando sus metadatos ocultos.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="map-side-note note-right-small-node">
        <svg class="marker-arrow" viewBox="0 0 120 80">
          <path d="M-20,40 Q30,35 110,40" stroke="#d3d3d3" stroke-width="7.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <path d="M80,15 L112,41 L80,65" stroke="#d3d3d3" stroke-width="7.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="note-text-block">
          <span class="service-title-handwritten">CRAWLERS</span>
          <span class="map-handwritten-text">Exploradores de<br>esquemas activos</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="node node-large node-glue">
      <div class="node-content">
        <img src="/glue-logo.png" alt="Glue" class="node-logo" />
      </div>
      <div class="node-popup popup-left">
        <div class="popup-header">
          <span class="popup-deity">Hermes</span>
          <span class="popup-aws-badge">AWS Glue</span>
        </div>
        <p class="popup-body">Orquestador ETL encargado de transformar y mensajear los flujos de datos entre capas.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="map-side-note note-right-large-node">
        <svg class="marker-arrow" viewBox="0 0 120 80">
          <path d="M-20,40 Q30,35 110,40" stroke="#d3d3d3" stroke-width="7.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <path d="M80,15 L112,41 L80,65" stroke="#d3d3d3" stroke-width="7.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="note-text-block">
          <span class="service-title-handwritten">GLUE</span>
          <span class="map-handwritten-text">El mensajero y ETL<br>de los datos</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="node node-medium node-athena">
      <div class="node-content">
        <img src="/athena-logo.png" alt="Athena" class="node-logo" />
      </div>
      <div class="node-popup popup-left">
        <div class="popup-header">
          <span class="popup-deity">Atenea</span>
          <span class="popup-aws-badge">AWS Athena</span>
        </div>
        <p class="popup-body">Motor de análisis interactivo que ejecuta consultas estructuradas SQL directas sobre S3.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="map-side-note note-right-medium-node">
        <svg class="marker-arrow" viewBox="0 0 120 80">
          <path d="M-20,40 Q30,35 110,40" stroke="#d3d3d3" stroke-width="7.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <path d="M80,15 L112,41 L80,65" stroke="#d3d3d3" stroke-width="7.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="note-text-block">
          <span class="service-title-handwritten">ATHENA</span>
          <span class="map-handwritten-text">Consultas ágiles<br>con sabiduría</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="node node-small node-final">
      <div class="node-content">
        <img src="/demo-logo.png" alt="Demo" class="node-logo" />
      </div>
      <div class="node-popup popup-left">
        <div class="popup-header">
          <span class="popup-deity">Efesto</span>
          <span class="popup-aws-badge">Demo App</span>
        </div>
        <p class="popup-body">La forja definitiva donde confluyen los flujos de datos expuestos en su interfaz funcional.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="map-side-note note-right-small-node">
        <svg class="marker-arrow" viewBox="0 0 120 80">
          <path d="M-20,40 Q30,35 110,40" stroke="#d3d3d3" stroke-width="7.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <path d="M80,15 L112,41 L80,65" stroke="#d3d3d3" stroke-width="7.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="note-text-block">
          <span class="service-title-handwritten">DEMO</span>
          <span class="map-handwritten-text">Ecosistema forjado<br>en armonía</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
/* WRAPPER */
.architecture-wrapper {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  min-height: 1300px;
  background: #222222;
  overflow: hidden;
  padding: 60px 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

.architecture-wrapper::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  top: 120px;
  bottom: 180px;
  left: 50%;
  width: 5px;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom,
    rgba(255,255,255,0.15),
    rgba(255,255,255,0.8) 50%,
    rgba(255,255,255,0.15)
  );
  background-size: 100% 200%;
  animation: solidPulseFlow 3s linear infinite;
  z-index: 1;
}

@keyframes solidPulseFlow {
  0%   { background-position: 0% 0%; }
  100% { background-position: 0% -200%; }
}

/* ─── TARJETA INFO ─────────────────────────────────── */
/* Bajada a 220px para dejar el logo completamente libre */
.info-intro-card {
  position: absolute;
  top: 220px;
  left: 40px;
  width: 310px;
  z-index: 10;
}

.card-shadow {
  position: absolute;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  top: 8px;
  left: 8px;
  z-index: 1;
}

.card-content {
  position: relative;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  padding: 24px 22px 22px;
  z-index: 2;
  color: #ffffff;
  border-radius: 2px;
  backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
}

.card-main-title {
  font-family: 'Caveat', cursive;
  font-size: 34px;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: #ffffff;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  margin: 0 0 12px 0;
  line-height: 1.05;
}

.card-subtitle-hint {
  font-size: 15px;
  line-height: 1.55;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  margin: 0 0 14px 0;
}

.card-hover-cta {
  font-family: 'Caveat', cursive;
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #ffffff;
  line-height: 1.3;
  margin: 0 0 18px 0;
  padding: 11px 14px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  border-left: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  animation: ctaBlink 2.8s ease-in-out infinite;
}

@keyframes ctaBlink {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; border-left-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); }
  50%       { opacity: 0.45; border-left-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); }
}

.analogy-box {
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  padding-top: 16px;
}

.handwritten-title {
  font-family: 'Caveat', cursive;
  font-size: 30px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #ffffff;
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  line-height: 1.1;
}

.analogy-body {
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
  margin: 0;
}

/* ─── SVG RAMAS ───────────────────────────────────── */
.architecture-lines {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; left: 0;
  width: 100%; height: 100%;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 2;
}

.side-map-line { fill: none; stroke-width: 4px; }
.static-base   { stroke: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); }

.pulse-diagonal {
  stroke: url(#diagonal-pulse-gradient);
  stroke-dasharray: 60 120;
  animation: svgPulseFlow 3s linear infinite;
}

@keyframes svgPulseFlow {
  0%   { stroke-dashoffset: 180; }
  100% { stroke-dashoffset: 0; }
}

/* ─── NODOS ───────────────────────────────────────── */
.node {
  position: absolute;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  z-index: 5;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.node-content {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%; height: 100%;
  border-radius: 999px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  background: #ffffff;
  border: 2px solid #000000;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  padding: 15px;
  transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 1, 0.5, 1);
}

.node:hover .node-content {
  box-shadow: 0 0 32px 12px rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
  transform: scale(1.05);
}

.node-logo { width: 62%; height: 62%; object-fit: contain; }

/* ─── POPUPS — estética web: gris claro, tipografía limpia ── */
.node-popup {
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
  width: 255px;
  background: #f4f4f4;
  border: 1.5px solid #cccccc;
  padding: 0;
  opacity: 0;
  pointer-events: none;
  transition: all 0.25s ease;
  color: #111111;
  box-shadow: 6px 6px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  text-align: left;
  z-index: 30;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.node:hover .node-popup { opacity: 1; }
.node-popup.popup-left  { right: 128%; }
.node-popup.popup-right { left: 128%; }

/* Cabecera: fondo gris muy oscuro, tipografía blanca */
.popup-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 12px 16px 10px;
  border-bottom: 1.5px solid #cccccc;
  background: #222222;
}

/* Nombre del dios en Caveat blanco */
.popup-deity {
  font-family: 'Caveat', cursive;
  font-size: 32px;
  font-weight: 800;
  font-style: italic;
  color: #ffffff;
  line-height: 1;
}

/* Badge neutro */
.popup-aws-badge {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #ffffff;
  background: #555555;
  padding: 4px 9px;
  border-radius: 2px;
  white-space: nowrap;
  align-self: center;
}

/* Cuerpo popup: fondo gris claro como la web */
.popup-body {
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 1.55;
  color: #333333;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 13px 16px 15px;
  background: #f4f4f4;
}

/* ─── NOTAS MANUSCRITAS DEL MAPA ─────────────────── */
.note-text-block {
  display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  text-align: left; width: 220px;
}

.service-title-handwritten {
  font-family: 'Caveat', cursive;
  font-size: 30px;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: #ffffff;
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

.map-handwritten-text {
  font-family: 'Caveat', cursive;
  font-size: 24px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: #c5c5c5;
  line-height: 1.2;
}

/* ─── FLECHAS Y POSICIONES ───────────────────────── */
.marker-arrow { width: 50px; flex-shrink: 0; overflow: visible; }

.map-side-note {
  position: absolute; top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
  display: flex; align-items: center;
  pointer-events: none; gap: 14px;
}

.note-right-large-node  { right: -290px; flex-direction: row; }
.note-right-medium-node { right: -278px; flex-direction: row; }
.note-right-small-node  { right: -268px; flex-direction: row; }

.note-left-small-node { left: -268px; flex-direction: row-reverse; }
.note-left-small-node .note-text-block { text-align: right; }
.reverse-arrow { transform: rotate(180deg); }

/* ─── TAMAÑOS DE NODO ────────────────────────────── */
.node-large  { width: 170px; height: 170px; }
.node-medium { width: 150px; height: 150px; }
.node-small  { width: 135px; height: 135px; }

/* ─── POSICIONES EJE VERTICAL ────────────────────── */
.node-s3      { top: 40px; }
.node-buckets { top: 320px; }
.node-glue    { top: 690px; }
.node-athena  { top: 920px; }
.node-final   { top: 1120px; }

/* ─── RAMAS LATERALES ────────────────────────────── */
.node-side-left  { left: 32%; transform: translateX(-50%); }
.node-side-right { left: 68%; transform: translateX(-50%); }

.node-iam      { top: 160px; }
.node-lambda   { top: 505px; }
.node-crawlers { top: 505px; }

/* ─── RESPONSIVE ─────────────────────────────────── */
@media (max-width: 1100px) {
  .architecture-wrapper { min-height: 2400px; padding-top: 520px; }
  .architecture-wrapper::before { display: none; }
  .info-intro-card {
    position: absolute;
    top: 20px; left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 85%;
  }
  .node { left: 50% !important; transform: translateX(-50%) !important; }
  .node-side-left  { top: 1260px !important; }
  .node-side-right { top: 1480px !important; }
  .node-final      { top: 1700px !important; }
  .map-side-note   { display: none; }
  .architecture-lines { display: none; }
}
</style>
